title: Ring of Fire - December 21 2013
description:
December 21, 2013
Ring of Fire 
Hosted by Robert F. Kennedy Jr., Mike Papantonio and Sam Seder


This week on Ring of Fire Radio:  Congressman Peter DeFazio will explain why he was one of the few Democrats to vote against the Ryan-Murray budget.

Rolling Stone's Matt Taibbi will be here to talk about the latest Wall Street scams.

Salon.com contributor David Dayen will explain the countless problems with the budget deal.

Author Les Leopold will tell us how cities across the country are fighting back against greedy Wall Street bankers.

And Tim Dickinson from Rolling Stone will discuss the good and bad things that have happened with gun control in the last year.
